  "importantNotice": {
    "de": "Um den Bonus des <b>Sauerhammer</b>-Sets zu nutzen, müsst ihr euch mit einer der folgenden Waffen ausrüsten:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27540::Sauerhammer}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27539::Sauersichel}}</color>",
    "en": "To get the <b>Bitter-Hammer</b> set bonus, equip one of these weapons:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27540::Bitter Hammer}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27539::Bitter Billhook}}</color>",
    "es": "Para disfrutar del bonus del set de los <b>Martilloseco</b>, equípate alguna de estas armas:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27540::Martillo seco}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27539::Hoz seca}}</color>",
    "fr": "",
    "id": "1104195",
    "pt": "Para se beneficiar do bônus do conjunto dos <b>Martelos Amargos</b>, equipe uma destas armas:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27540::Martelo Amargo}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27539::Podadeira Amarga}}</color>"
  },
